snippet.title: Rise of Jericho - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
✨ Wishlist Rise of Jericho now! ⬇️
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2363570/Rise_of_Jericho/
Epic: https://store.epicgames.com/es-ES/p/rise-of-jericho-cb083c

Lead hunter-gatherers and give rise to human civilization in Jericho, the oldest city in the world. Gather resources, craft tools and build structures to protect villagers and make your city thrive.

Developed by Sudaka Games

Rise of Jericho is launching on June 9 🗓
